Jaimee Foxworth https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jaimee_Foxworth 0 Jaimee Monae Foxworth (born December 17, 1979) is an American actress and model. She is best known for her role of Judy Winslow, the younger daughter of Carl and Harriette Winslow on the ABC/CBS sitcom Family Matters.
